parameters.name: R
parameters.description:
Heliocentric range from Sun to spacecraft 
                        in units of astronomical units (1 AU = 149674000 km).

parameters.name: LAT
parameters.description:
Spacecraft heliocentric latitude, 
                        the angle between the plane containing the
                        solar spin axis and the solar equatorial plane
                       (positive above the equatorial plane), in degrees.

parameters.name: LON
parameters.description:
Spacecraft heliocentric longitude,
                        (increasing in the direction of planetary orbital motion)
